Italian Troops Out Of Iraq
Newly elected Italian Prime Minister Romano Prodi said that the
invasion of Iraq was a "grave error" and will propose withdrawing
Italian troops. What do you think?
Old Man
Jorge Previn,
Bouncer
"Fuck! Now I have to throw out my Italian wine, too?"
Young Woman
Sue Maines,
Bike Mechanic
"I just hope they don't close that charming Iraqi-Italian place in
Fallujah where Mahmoud and I first fell in love."
Asian Man
Andre Wilson,
Exterminator
"But who's gonna get all hot-blooded when the Iraqis insult our troops'
honor?"
